# Ship pre-built Sunspot circuit artefacts so the issuer-service Dockerfile
# can bake them into the image without needing nargo/sunspot at build time.
# Re-include the dir, re-exclude its contents, then whitelist the 3 artefacts
# the runtime needs (ACIR JSON, gnark CCS, Groth16 proving key).
!circuits/target/
circuits/target/*
!circuits/target/zksettle_slice.json
!circuits/target/zksettle_slice.ccs
!circuits/target/zksettle_slice.pk
